@startuml activity_mode_toggle

|User|
|CalculatorWindow|
|GUISessionAdapter|

|User|
start
:Click mode toggle button;

|CalculatorWindow|
:_on_mode_toggle_clicked()
Determine new_mode:
  if _current_mode == "normal"
    new_mode = "scientific"
  else
    new_mode = "normal";

:on_mode_changed(new_mode)
Clear _pending_binary_op = None
Clear _display_value = "";

|GUISessionAdapter|
:set_mode(new_mode)
→ CalculatorSession.set_mode(new_mode)
Reload _operation_list for new mode;

|CalculatorWindow|
:_current_mode = new_mode
update_operation_buttons();

:Destroy existing _ops_frame children
Re-create 4-column operations grid
with ops for new_mode
Re-bind hover effects on each button;

:Update mode toggle button label;

stop

@enduml
